    "# Sentiment Classification: LSTM vs Transformer vs BERT\n",
    "**Prof. Ing. Carlos Andrés Sierra, M.Sc. — Universidad Distrital FJC**\n",
    "\n",
    "Practical example from the *Deep Learning: Foundations* slides — *Sequence Models & Transformers* section.\n",
    "\n",
    "Compares three architectures trained on the **IMDB** dataset (50 k reviews, binary sentiment):\n",
    "\n",
    "| Model | Description |\n",
    "|-------|-------------|\n",
    "| **Model A — LSTM** | 2-layer bidirectional LSTM + Embedding + FC head |\n",
    "| **Model B — Transformer** | Small encoder: 4 heads, 2 layers + positional encoding + FC head |\n",
    "| **Model C — BERT** | `bert-base-uncased` fine-tuned (HuggingFace) |\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Expected result:** BERT ≫ Transformer ≥ LSTM with the same training budget.\n"
   ]
